@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.60 * v1 + 0.86) * (v2 + 0.02 * tmp + 0.72)) + (wp.sin(v2 + 0.86) / 0.50))
    v0 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.24 / v1 + 0.40) * (v2 + 0.94 / tmp + 0.72)))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.66)) * wp.abs(wp.abs(v2 + 0.27)))
    v1 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
